{"tid":208033,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"喉嚨痛如何分辦係唔係細菌性?","createTime":"2017-04-19T09:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T10:07:26.000Z","uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aea7e3da1b3b05137074fc373b5f7c6c31dca12a","tid":208033,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:24:29.000Z","msg":"想知一般喉嚨痛要有咩病徵先決定食唔食抗生素<br />\n<br />\n事源係<br />\n我睇醫生佢開左Augmentin 625 mg<br />\n佢話可以等過兩日未有好轉<br />\n等我鬼識睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n家下我對住塊鐘鏡用燈照有d白色<br />\n好似痱滋既野係喉嚨<br />\n吞口水痛到仆街"},{"pid":"35ddee188f6bb55dc0968cafa7d32dacadb4c12e","tid":208033,"uid":10973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:25:56.000Z","msg":"呢d好似係發炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"732c3908d9d946a75367889dc200dc0008b7eed4","tid":208033,"uid":52494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:29:40.000Z","msg":"前排同你一樣，食左幾日消炎藥就好番"},{"pid":"c6427fac8eff66f8fedf06eb00a38230fca3834b","tid":208033,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:29:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d好似係發炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁點先係細菌性?"},{"pid":"58ba6c10d50396ccd12798873a1e5eb9079b3529","tid":208033,"uid":104392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:58:24.000Z","msg":"細菌性通常快黎快去，病毒就慢慢攪你流幾星期鼻水<br />\n<br />\n最主要分都係睇禁落頸度痛唔痛同喉嚨顏色<br />\n<br />\n痛方面， 通常bacterial pharyngitis 禁條頸會痛， 因為淋巴腫哂， 肌肉都痛： myalgia。 病毒就較少頸痛。<br />\n<br />\n紅腫熱痛就一定嫁啦<br />\n但細菌通常tonsils, uvula 都紅得好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勁咪有膿黃黃地 白白地咁。 病毒就少少紅<br />\n<br />\nlab test 就好易分， 但睇症狀實差唔多嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9284a3450ae5662c401b7dc6919c2883bef3b8a0","tid":208033,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:05:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細菌性通常快黎快去，病毒就慢慢攪你流幾星期鼻水<br />\n<br />\n最主要分都係睇禁落頸度痛唔痛同喉嚨顏色<br />\n<br />\n痛方面， 通常bacterial pharyngitis 禁條頸會痛， 因為淋巴腫哂， 肌肉都痛： myalgia。 病毒就較少頸痛。<br />\n<br />\n紅腫熱痛就一定嫁啦<br />\n但細菌通常tonsils, uvula 都紅得好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勁咪有膿黃黃地 白白地咁。 病毒就少少紅<br />\n<br />\nlab test 就好易分， 但睇症狀實差唔多嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\ntonsillitis 真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但黎得快，去得都好快。大約兩日就完了"},{"pid":"c85630df76ce1ca3cfb3202041daf27418af26ea","tid":208033,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:07:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細菌性通常快黎快去，病毒就慢慢攪你流幾星期鼻水<br />\n<br />\n最主要分都係睇禁落頸度痛唔痛同喉嚨顏色<br />\n<br />\n痛方面， 通常bacterial pharyngitis 禁條頸會痛， 因為淋巴腫哂， 肌肉都痛： myalgia。 病毒就較少頸痛。<br />\n<br />\n紅腫熱痛就一定嫁啦<br />\n但細菌通常tonsils, uvula 都紅得好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勁咪有膿黃黃地 白白地咁。 病毒就少少紅<br />\n<br />\nlab test 就好易分， 但睇症狀實差唔多嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喉嚨痛黎得好激<br />\n星期一黎 今日痛到仆街<br />\n無鼻水 都無感冒徵狀<br />\n但淋巴未有腫痛<br />\ntonsils, uvula唔識睇同平時有無分別<br />\n<br />\n咁係痛毒性多?"}]}